, e allo Splendid di Brooklin. Per un banale errore di stampa, alcune copie ( 15 circa) presentano una serigrafia a colori, al posto della classica bianco e nero, e verranno date esclusivamente alle persone che acquisteranno l\'album via maledetto.it.</p><p> </p></body></html>','<html><head></head><body><p>Father Murphy, before falling in love with him, denied his own Christ 8 times :</p><p>1-the trigger </p><p>2-nothing wrong </p><p>3-liquid center (christmas time)</p><p>4-XI sunset </p><p>5-some guitars are hard to play </p><p>6-rollercoaster </p><p>7-american coffee </p><p>8-warnings (waves) </p><p>Recorded between New york City and Venice (Italy), summer 00, winter/spring 2001.<br />Produced and flavoured by Vicar Vittorio Demarin.</p><p>Then Father Murphy approached the religion, learning by heart the Holy Scriptures.</p><p>APRIL 2005 NEWS: on the occasion of the fifth repressing, the record comes now with a new bonus track: fragment of an old Father Murphy show, recorded live in april 2002 at Continental, NYC, and Splendid Bar, Brooklin. Due to a common mistake, few copies present a colorfull serigraphie, instead of the usual b/w one: first Paypal orders will satisfy you collectors!</p></body></html>','2005-01-20','99','2159','2','0');
INSERT INTO `album_order` VALUES ('5','1','','Estate Rock - Legnago 2003','5','','','<html><head></head><body><br /></body></html>','<html><head></head><body><br /></body></html>','<html><head></head><body><p><strong>Questa compilation comprende i 12 gruppi che sono stati selezionati per il concorso di Verona \"Legnago Rock\". </strong></p><p>Potete trovare anche la canzone di Littlebrown che si è classificato terzo. Attenzione, per un errore è stato scritto <strong>Worm love</strong> come titolo, in realtà la canzone è: <strong>\"Kiss 1\"</strong>. Ci sono dei gruppi interessanti e dei gruppi un po\' più pop, ma nel complesso è una buona compilation. </p><p>12 gruppi a 3 euro. </p><p>baci </p><p>P.S. se interessato mandaci una mail, risponderemo con tutte le informazioni necessarie.</p></body></html>','<html><head></head><body><p><strong>This compilation includes 12 bands selected for \"Legnago Rock\" Verona\'s contest.</strong></p><p>Inside, there is a Littlebrown song, and he rich the 3rd position with that song. Attention, who made the compilation rear cover did a mistake writing the song title: <strong>Kiss 1</strong>, not Worm love.<br />There are some interesting bands, and some bands suck. But the compilation is not that bad.</p><p>12 bands for 3 euro</p><p>kisses</p><p>P.S. if interested in this compilation, send us a mail, we reply with all the informations.</p><p>If you live in Usa, send a mail to our NYC branch director, RDN, <a href=\"mailto:urizen1@earthlink.net\">urizen1@earthlink.net</a> </p></body></html>','2005-01-20','0','0','2','');
INSERT INTO `album_order` VALUES ('28','21','Bob Corn','We don\'t need the outside','12','MDCP063','Bob-copertina3.jpg','Il nuovo disco di <span style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Bob Corn</span>, <span style=\"FONT-STYLE: italic\">We don\'t need the outside</span>, esce in vinile 12\'\' grazie alla collaborazione tra <span style=\"FONT-STYLE: italic\">Madcap, Boring Machines, Here i stay Recs e Smartz Records</span>...e ovviamente <span style=\"FONT-STYLE: italic\">Fooltribe</span>...<br />E\' finalmente possibile ordinarlo anche tramite il nostro mailorder, andate comunque a cercare dove suonerà Bob Corn nella vostra città, perchè tanto prima o poi si farà tutta l\'Italia, in lungo e in largo, isole comprese!','<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Bob Corn</span>\'s new record, <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">We don\'t need the outisde</span>, have been released in a 12\'\' vinyl by a bunch of italian indiependet label, including Madcap, Boring Machines, Here i stay Recs and Smartz Records...plus Fooltribe, of course.<br />','<p><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\"><strong>we don\'t need the outside<br /></strong>10 tracks 33 min</font></font></p>\r\n<font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">\r\n<p><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">1. cold and gold<br />2. the hottest autumn ever<br />3. rose of my past<br />4. reds between blacks                  </font><br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">5. my sweet, we\'re bright</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">6. peace in the storm</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">7. come to me</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">8. with you</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">9. everything but nothing</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">10. wearing wings</font> </p>\r\n<p>Ed ecco la pagina dedicata a Bob Corn <a href=\"http://www.maledetto.it/artists.php?idArtist=21\">http://www.maledetto.it/artists.php?idArtist=21</a></p>\r\n</font>','<p><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\"><strong>we don\'t need the outside<br /></strong>10 tracks 33 min</font></font></p>\r\n<p><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">1. cold and gold<br />2. the hottest autumn ever<br />3. rose of my past<br />4. reds between blacks                  </font><br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">5. my sweet, we\'re bright</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">6. peace in the storm</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">7. come to me</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">8. with you</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">9. everything but nothing</font> <br /><font face=\"MS Sans Serif\" size=\"2\">10. wearing wings</font> </p>\r\n<p>Here\'s Bob Corn page: <a href=\"http://www.maledetto.it/artists.php?idArtist=21\">http://www.maledetto.it/artists.php?idArtist=21</a></p>','2007-10-31','1','498','0','0');
INSERT INTO `album_order` VALUES ('6','1***2***7***4***8','','Fucking fuck compilation #1','5','','','','','<html><body><p>La prima compilation della <strong>Madcap records </strong>è stata realizzata nell\' Aprile 2003, in collaborazione con il cafe La Pausa, in occasione di una personale di Denis Dotto.<br />All\' interno sono presenti 4 progetti (<strong>Littlebrown, Oswald, F.Murphy</strong> e <strong>Blaster- in realtà lo stesso</strong> Denis Dotto e Chiara Lee) per un totale di 7 canzoni inedite, e 27 tavole di Denis Dotto.<br /><br />Se  interessato, puoi comprare la compilation a <font color=\"#ff0000\"><strong>5 € spese di spedizioni incluse</strong></font>. <br />Mandaci una mail, e ti daremo le indicazioni necessarie.</p></body></html>','<html><body><p>The first <strong>Madcap Records compilation</strong> was released in April 2003, in collaboration with La Pausa Cafè (soudtrack for  Denis Dotto \'s art opening). <br />Inside, there are 4 projects (<strong>Littlebrown, Oswald, F.Murphy</strong> and <strong>Blaster</strong>, Denis Dotto & Chiara Lee) including 7 unreleased songs, and 27 Denis Dotto\'s paints.</p><p>If you are interested about, you can buy the compilation for <font color=\"#ff0000\"><strong>5€ shipping costs included</strong></font>.<br />Send a mail and we reply with all the informations.</p><p>If you live in USA, send a mail to our NYC branch director, RDN, <a href=\"mailto:urizen1@earthlink.net\">urizen1@earthlink.net</a>  </p></body></html>','2005-01-20','0','15','2','');
